about it and he's singing

20:10.069 --> 20:14.223
all of his emotions at
Leif this very second.

20:14.513 --> 20:17.575
♪ Frightening ♪

20:17.818 --> 20:20.770
- ♪ Well, I... ♪
- No, he's not.

20:21.378 --> 20:23.497
Dude doesn't have a care in the world.

20:26.261 --> 20:30.308
♪ With my head in my hands,
I sit and cry ♪

20:30.333 --> 20:32.348
I strongly disagree with you.

20:32.373 --> 20:33.581
♪ Don't speak ♪

20:33.606 --> 20:36.780
♪ I know what you're thinking ♪

20:36.804 --> 20:39.717
♪ And I don't need your reasons ♪

20:39.741 --> 20:43.176
♪ Don't tell me 'cause it hurts ♪

20:43.645 --> 20:45.622
Max, believe me,

20:45.647 --> 20:48.525
Tobin... is heartbroken.

20:48.550 --> 20:51.308
Okay, let's just end this
insanity once and for all.

20:51.333 --> 20:53.063
Hey, Tobin. You good?

20:53.087 --> 20:55.284
Your mama thought so last night.

20:55.309 --> 20:57.794
