26:42.147 --> 26:45.356
then... I think we
gotta stop hanging out.

26:49.504 --> 26:51.348
Max, don't go. I can prove it.

26:51.373 --> 26:53.151
No, you can't! There's no way to prove

26:53.176 --> 26:54.700
