26:59.884 --> 27:02.239
After I got the power...

27:02.837 --> 27:04.692
you sang to me.

27:05.170 --> 27:07.181
Love songs.

27:07.206 --> 27:09.067
Lots of love songs.

27:09.910 --> 27:11.624
I did?

27:11.649 --> 27:13.036
Yeah.

27:13.061 --> 27:16.645
